      "message": "hey, i heard to like avoiding allocs. Here is an idea:\n\nswap all shall invocations to the end of slice:\n\nr :\u003d len(invs) - 1\nfor l, inv :\u003d range invs{\n  if l \u003e\u003d r{ break }\n  if inv.Status \u003d\u003d \"\" {invs[r] \u003d inv; r-- }\n}\n...\n... datastore.Get(c, invs[r:])...",
